room_title: Escape room "The Pharaoh's Tomb" by The Cube Escape Rooms in Santa Barbara
room_description:
Mankind waited for death through the curse of the mummy of Amenhotep, and therefore the priests began a ritual to be completed during the parade of planets.
Unfortunately, the priests did not finish the ritual and our world is still in danger. Now the destiny is in your hands, brave explorers! You must find the 12 zodiac signs hidden in the tomb. And with the help of zodiac circle â€“ complete the ritual. Humanity will be saved from an imminent disaster, and your names will always remain on the pages of the history. You have 1 hour.
